This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it focuses on the development of NLP-based on-line contentware applications. It could also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as the applications are designed to process and analyze textual data. Additionally, the paper may fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as NLP is a subfield of both these categories. Finally, the paper may also be relevant to cs.SE (Software Engineering) as it discusses the development process and constraints of producing these applications.
